strategy_rules: Prioritize micro cap tokens (<100k) - these averaged +14.7% ROI with a 60.0% win rate
Require buy ratio >= 1.5 - trades with ratio <1.5 averaged lower ROI
Avoid mid cap tokens (500k-2M) - these averaged -57.8% ROI with a 0.0% win rate
Favor tokens with age between 6-24h - 55.6% of these trades were winners
Avoid tokens with extremely high 1h change at entry (>100%) - these often resulted in significant losses
Require vol spike >0.05x for consideration - lower vol spikes often resulted in losses
Avoid tokens older than 24h - only 1 trade older than 24h was profitable
avoid_conditions: AVOID tokens already pumped >100% in 1h (lost -29.8% on テディベア (TEDDY))
